{"id": "1413898778489917482", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "author_id": "645758482305253422", "author_name": "duxadidus", "content": "How do you play Corposant in Chapter 7? Because the logic is simple. My strategy is to give the blessing of fertility to the cost 4 Corpo and the cost 1 Doresain.\n\nAnd rather than using my Corpo as a tank, it becomes subDPS, since all the Strength bonuses given by the Caro realm boost its tentacle damage so that it cost 4.\n\nAlso worth mentioning is that Salvador gives him Gluttony, a wheel that increases maximum health in exchange for an Orison. This way you increase the amount of Furnace and with it the shields that its cost 2 can give you.\n\nYour team is not a bad one, I'd just like to know how you play.", "timestamp": "2025-09-06T14:48:57.761000+00:00", "type": 19, "mentions": ["588028137099624450"], "reply_to": "1413856790596030484"}
